{"tid":1210832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔高登64  集體失憶〕613慘案六週年","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:32:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14f61ba0350752a86946af83df308467c8ca7fa5","tid":1210832,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20130614152729/evchk/images/d/dc/Housenews_613_bam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20130614152729%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fdc%2FHousenews_613_bam.jpg&h=8d485891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n613大量高登會員被封禁事件，又稱613大屠殺事件、613事件，是繼1028高登大量會員被封禁事件後第二次高登版的六四事件，發生於2013年6月13日，當日有大量高登會員發現自己帳號被封禁（BAM），肇事會員已超過500人，刪post至少400多個，為高登有紀錄以來封禁最多人及刪post最多的一次。期間一眾被封禁會員紛紛借用其它高登帳號，上站務台質問高登管理員。 <br />\n<br />\n林祖舜事後在「高登公告」證實，大規模封禁會員是與會員對某傳媒企業的言論或涉誹謗有關。 <br />\n<br />\n613慘案wiki <br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/613%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81%E7%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F613%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2yxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=4c4cd786\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/613%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81%E7%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"b053895e9de58ebfe95b5545fab34125bf2340b5","tid":1210832,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"重要時刻<br />\n垃圾POST唔好回 <br />\n再回死全家"}]}